msgid ""
"Influence is a numeric multiplier used in ordering search results. A "
"higher number means the corresponding factor has more influence on "
"search results; zero means the factor is ignored. Changing these "
"numbers does not require the search index to be rebuilt. Changes take "
"effect immediately."
msgstr ""
"Mõju on otsingutulemuste järjestamisel kasutatav arvuline kordaja. "
"Mida suurem number, seda suurem on vastava teguri mõju "
"otsingutulemustele; null tähendab, et tegurit eiratakse. Nende "
"numbrite muutmine ei nõua otsinguindeksi uuesti koostamist. "
"Muudatused jõustuvad kohe."

