"approval)"
msgstr ""
"Kasutajakonto [user:display-name] detailid lehel [site:name] (ootab "
"administraatori kinnitust)"

msgid ""
"[user:display-name] has applied for an account.\n"
"\n"
"[user:edit-url]"
msgstr ""
"[user:display-name] on kontole kandideerinud.\n"
"\n"
"[user:edit-url]"

