msgstr "Lisa ja paigalda mooduleid, et laiendada saidi funktsionaalsust."

msgid "Some required modules must be installed"
msgstr "Mõned vajalikud moodulid peavad olema installitud"

msgid ""
"Install the <em>Automated Cron</em> module to allow cron execution at "
