"takistada automatiseeritud tarkvara teie saidil väärkasutust "
"tegevast tegevusest. Samal ajal lubab see teie seaduslikel kasutajatel "
"mugavalt läbi pääseda."

msgid "Administer reCAPTCHA settings."
msgstr "Halda reCAPTCHA seadeid."

msgid "reCAPTCHA settings"
msgstr "reCAPTCHA seaded"

msgid "The size of CAPTCHA to serve."
msgstr "CAPTCHA suurus."

msgid "@info"
msgstr "@info"

msgid "Protects and defends"
msgstr "Kaitseb ja kaitsleb"

msgid ""
"reCAPTCHA is built for security. Armed with state of the art "
"technology, it always stays at the forefront of spam and abuse "
"fighting trends. reCAPTCHA is on guard for you, so you can rest easy."
msgstr ""
"reCAPTCHA on loodud turvalisust silmas pidades. Olles varustatud "
"tipptasemel tehnoloogiaga, hoiab see alati sammu rämpsposti ja "
"väärkasutuse vastaste trendidega. reCAPTCHA valvab sinu eest, nii et "
"saad muretult rahus olla."

msgid ""
"You will now find a reCAPTCHA tab in the CAPTCHA administration page "
