"'composer/composer:@version'</code>, <em>või</em> lisa järgmine rida "
"faili <code>settings.php</code>: "
"<code>$settings['package_manager_composer_path'] = "
"'@composer_path';</code>. Lisateabe saamiseks vaata <a "
"href=\":url\">seda muudatuselogit</a>."

msgid "Path to <code>rsync</code> is configured"
