msgstr "Valitud veebivormidel on kokku @total esitamist."

msgid ""
"You may not delete these webforms until there is less than @batch "
"total submissions."
msgstr ""
"Te ei tohi neid veebivorme kustutada, kuni esitatud formularide "
"koguarv on väiksem kui @batch."

